\underbrace{=}_{\mathbf{p} = m \mathbf{v}} \sum_j \mathbf{F}_j \cdot \mathbf{r}_j + 2 \sum_j \frac{1}{2} m_j \mathbf{v}_j^2 \tag{2}\]

